data.title: Books and Books Key West
data.meta_description: Key West’s local, nonprofit, independent bookstore — a community center for readers and writers.
data.meta_site_name: Books & Books - Key West's Independent Bookstore
data.text:
Our August featured staff pick: The God of the Woods by Liz Moore, picked by assistant manager Sara. “I couldn’t put this book down – the perfect summer mystery read! It had me all the way until the last sentence!”

Do you want to know who exactly is the literary a**hole in any given situation? Author Kristen Arnett can help. She writes the Literary Hub, Am I the Literary A**hole? column and will be doing a live event based on the column, September 13 at The Studios of Key West.
